#

Savory Garlic Butter Shrimp

20 min
$12
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseAppetizer

Tags:

QuickEasySeafoodSavory

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a rich garlic butter sauce, ready in just 20 minutes!

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • parsley (chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
